$ CSS: font property

The `font` allows to combine the values of a few font related properties:
  • `font-style`
  • `font-variant`
  • `font-weight`
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/font/size[`font-size`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/font-family[`font-family`]

